# Aquatiq Root Container Environment Configuration
# ============================================================================
# üîê SECURITY UPDATE: Credentials moved to Docker secrets!
# ============================================================================
# The following credentials are NO LONGER stored in this .env file:
# - POSTGRES_PASSWORD (now in secrets/postgres_password.txt)
# - REDIS_PASSWORD (now in secrets/redis_password.txt)
# - N8N_ENCRYPTION_KEY (now in secrets/n8n_encryption_key.txt)
# - TRAEFIK_DASHBOARD_AUTH (now in secrets/traefik_dashboard_auth.txt)
